text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to get an amazon standard identification number (asin)?
text.Response A: Sure, I can get you an ASIN for any product you want. Just tell me the product name or URL and I’ll get you the ASIN.
text.Response B: Sure, I can help you with that.  In order to get an ASIN, you’ll need to create an Amazon account, and then click on “Create an ASIN” from the “My Items” page.  After you do that, you’ll be given a page where you can enter information about your product, and then click “Create ASIN”.

428.displayed_text:
Prompt

Can you tell me how to get an amazon standard identification number (asin)?

Response A

Sure, I can get you an ASIN for any product you want. Just tell me the product name or URL and I’ll get you the ASIN.

Response B

Sure, I can help you with that. In order to get an ASIN, you’ll need to create an Amazon account, and then click on “Create an ASIN” from the “My Items” page. After you do that, you’ll be given a page where you can enter information about your product, and then click “Create ASIN”.
